## 🛠️ Usage

To run the full production training (3000+ iterations per model), use:

```bash
python3 heart_v6_pseudo_uci.py
```

The script will automatically detect the correct data paths in `Desktop/Istrazivanje` and generate a submission file named `submission_v6_pseudo_uci.csv`.

